FT  29 MAY 92 / Government Bonds: Benchmark Government Bonds
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Belgium, Denmark and Spain: Between April 30 and May 20 bond yields for
these markets supplied to the Financial Times and published here were
calculated on a semi-annual basis, rather than the annual basis which is the
local standard. Bond yields for this period recalculated on an annual basis
can be obtained by application to: Garry Hayes, Financial Times, 1 Southwark
Bridge, London, SE1 9HL.
The yield basis used in this table for the Italian government bond market
was changed from semi-annual to annual on May 20, to reflect the method more
commonly used in the market. For comparison purposes, yields for Italian
government bonds before May 20, recalculated on the same annual basis, can
be obtained by application to the same address.
