</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
In spite of a better second six months compared with the opening half,
full-year profits of the City of London PR Group, a USM-quoted provider of
specialist investor and press relation services, fell by 14.5 per cent to
Pounds 520,827 pre-tax.
