12 months ago, boosted turnover for the year to end-March from Pounds
689,000 to Pounds 2.19m.
The IRB offshoots made a small profit in the final quarter but are budgeted
to make a 'significant contribution' for the year ahead.
Earnings emerged at 4.78p (4.9p). The dividend for the year is being lifted
to 3.18p (3.09p) via an increased final of 2.14p.
