interest costs of Pounds 1.47m (Pounds 1.75m). No figures were available for
net debt or gearing.
Although the family-controlled group lost 5.6p per share, against earnings
of 13.9p, the final dividend is maintained at 6.5p to give an unchanged
total of 11.5p, costing Pounds 473,000.
