includes BhS, Mothercare and Habitat.
Yesterday, the company announced a reshuffling of its senior management
which will lead to the departure of Mr Michael Harvey as chairman and chief
executive of Habitat and the promotion of two BhS directors who worked
closely with Mr Dworkin in turning round the clothing and houseware company.
Ms Ann Iverson, BhS's American stores director, who previously worked with
