<TEXT>
TWO of Japan's leading oil distributors, Mitsubishi Oil and Cosmos Oil,
yesterday announced record profits for the year to end-March.
Mitsubishi Oil said its 9.7 per cent rise in pre-tax profits to Y23.5bn
