Net profit grew by 22.9 per cent to Y13.6bn. The dividend was raised to Y8
from Y7.50.
Mitsubishi Oil expects higher sales, but lower pre-tax profits for the
current fiscal year.
Cosmos Oil had its best profits since its creation in 1986 as a result of
the merger of Daiky Oil and Maruzen Oil. Pre-tax earnings climbed by 55.5
per cent to Y27.8bn, while net profits surged by 90.6 per cent to Y19.4bn.
Sales fell by 7.7 per cent to Y1,581bn.
