FT  28 MAY 92 / Roddick puts the emphasis on the 'green'
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Ms Anita Roddick, the managing director of Body Shop International,
yesterday switched attention to the group's 'green' credentials. The move
came in the wake of controversy about its stance on the issue of animal
testing of cosmetics. At the retailer's first results press conference, Ms
